  1: # Java JSON Schema Generator – Module Swagger (2.x)
  2: [![Maven Central](https://maven-badges.herokuapp.com/maven-central/com.github.victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2/badge.svg)](https://maven-badges.herokuapp.com/maven-central/com.github.victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2)
  3: 
  4: Module for the [jsonschema-generator](../jsonschema-generator) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (2.x) annotations
  5: 
  6: ## Features
  7:  1. From `@Schema(description = …)` on types in general, derive `"description"`.
  8:  2. From `@Schema(title = …)` on types in general, derive `"title"`.
  9:  3. From `@Schema(ref = …)` on types in general, replace subschema with `"$ref"` to external/separate schema (except for the main type being targeted).
  10:  4. From `@Schema(subTypes = …)` on types in general, derive `"anyOf"` alternatives.
