ator)\n4: \n5: Creating JSON Schema (Draft 6, Draft 7, Draft 2019-09 or Draft 2020-12) from your Java classes utilising Jackson.\n6: \n7: ----\n8: \n9: This project consists of:\n---\n2: [![Build Status](https://github.com/victools/jsonschema-generator/workflows/Java%20CI%20(Maven)/badge.svg)](https://github.com/victools/jsonschema-generator/actions?query=workflow%3A%22Java+CI+%28Maven%29%22)\n3: [![Maven Central](https://maven-badges.herokuapp.com/maven-central/com.github.victools/jsonschema-generator/badge.svg)](https://maven-badges.herokuapp.com/maven-central/com.github.victools/jsonschema-generator)\n4: \n5: Creating JSON Schema (Draft 6, Draft 7, Draft 2019-09 or Draft 2020-12) from your Java classes utilising Jackson.\n6: \n7: ----\n8: \n9: This project consists of:\n10: - the [victools/jsonschema-generator](jsonschema-generator) (the only thing you need to get started)\n11: - a few modules bundling standard configurations for your convenience:\n---\n9: This project consists of:\n10: - the [victools/jsonschema-generator](jsonschema-generator) (the only thing you need to get started)\n11: - a few modules bundling standard configurations for your convenience:\n12:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jackson](jsonschema-module-jackson) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jackson` annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore) as well as looking up appropriate (annotated) subtypes\n13:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation](jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jakarta.validation.constraints` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n14:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-javax-validation](jsonschema-module-javax-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `javax.validation` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n15:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5](jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (1.5.x) annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"const\"/\"enum\")\n16:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2](jsonschema-module-swagger-2) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (2.x) `@Schema` annotations\n17: - the [victools/jsonschema-maven-plugin](jsonschema-maven-plugin) – allowing you to generate JSON Schemas as part of your Maven build\n18: \n---\n10: - the [victools/jsonschema-generator](jsonschema-generator) (the only thing you need to get started)\n11: - a few modules bundling standard configurations for your convenience:\n12:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jackson](jsonschema-module-jackson) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jackson` annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore) as well as looking up appropriate (annotated) subtypes\n13:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation](jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jakarta.validation.constraints` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n14:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-javax-validation](jsonschema-module-javax-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `javax.validation` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n15:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5](jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (1.5.x) annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"const\"/\"enum\")\n16:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2](jsonschema-module-swagger-2) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (2.x) `@Schema` annotations\n17: - the [victools/jsonschema-maven-plugin](jsonschema-maven-plugin) – allowing you to generate JSON Schemas as part of your Maven build\n18: \n19: Another example for such a module is:\n---\n11: - a few modules bundling standard configurations for your convenience:\n12:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jackson](jsonschema-module-jackson) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jackson` annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore) as well as looking up appropriate (annotated) subtypes\n13:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation](jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jakarta.validation.constraints` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n14:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-javax-validation](jsonschema-module-javax-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `javax.validation` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n15:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5](jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (1.5.x) annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"const\"/\"enum\")\n16:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2](jsonschema-module-swagger-2) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (2.x) `@Schema` annotations\n17: - the [victools/jsonschema-maven-plugin](jsonschema-maven-plugin) – allowing you to generate JSON Schemas as part of your Maven build\n18: \n19: Another example for such a module is:\n20: - [imIfOu/jsonschema-module-addon](https://github.com/imIfOu/jsonschema-module-addon) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from a custom annotation with various parameters, which is part of the module.\n---\n12:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jackson](jsonschema-module-jackson) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jackson` annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore) as well as looking up appropriate (annotated) subtypes\n13:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation](jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jakarta.validation.constraints` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n14:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-javax-validation](jsonschema-module-javax-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `javax.validation` annotations (e.g. which properties are nullable or not, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"minItems\"/\"maxItems\", \"minLength\"/\"maxLength\")\n15:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5](jsonschema-module-swagger-1.5) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (1.5.x) annotations (e.g. \"description\", property name overrides, what properties to ignore, their \"minimum\"/\"maximum\", \"const\"/\"enum\")\n16:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-swagger-2](jsonschema-module-swagger-2) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `swagger` (2.x) `@Schema` annotations\n17: - the [victools/jsonschema-maven-plugin](jsonschema-maven-plugin) – allowing you to generate JSON Schemas as part of your Maven build\n18: \n19: Another example for such a module is:\n20: - [imIfOu/jsonschema-module-addon](https://github.com/imIfOu/jsonschema-module-addon) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from a custom annotation with various parameters, which is part of the module.\n21: \n---\n13:     - [victools/jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation](jsonschema-module-jakarta-validation) – deriving JSON Schema attributes from `jakarta.validation.constraints` annotations (e.g. which 